#### Learning Contribution

| Property | Definition |
|----------|-----------|
| **What it is** | Whether this Memory has contributed to Learning. |
| **Cognitive role** | Enables learning tracing and meta-cognitive assessment. |

#### Decision Contribution

| Property | Definition |
|----------|-----------|
| **What it is** | Whether this Memory has informed a Recommendation or Decision. |
| **Cognitive role** | Enables decision tracing and Memory impact assessment. |

#### Narrative Contribution

| Property | Definition |
|----------|-----------|
| **What it is** | Whether this Memory has contributed to a Narrative. |
| **Cognitive role** | Enables narrative tracing and communication impact assessment. |

#### Complete Evolution History

| Property | Definition |
|----------|-----------|
| **What it is** | The complete record of this Memory's existence. |
